data.description: This gorgeous updated home features a split floorplan with 2 bedrooms sharing an adjacent bath with tub/shower combo.The spacious owners suite has high ceilings,ceiling fan & the adjacent restroom features a recent custom shower install,2 vanities with sinks in each + large soaking tub.The owners large closet has lots of storage & shelves for shoes.The closet conveniently connects to the utility room.The family room has hi ceilings,builtins adjacent to the fireplace,ceiling fan & a great view of the backyard.In 23' owners installed luxury vinyl plank in the family room,formal dining room & primary bedroom.The large kitchen features stainless appliances & huge island + breakfast bar. It has a great layout for entertaining & meal prep.The formal dining could be converted to a study game/guest room as the breakfast room could be used for family dining.Other features:Sprinkler system,security cameras,prewired for alarm system & generator interlock hookup.*Seller is brokers son*Plz measure.
